author: @rosimarymaria9825
content:
Life is a passage full of great opportunities. Anything can happen at any time, and we just need to be prepared to do our best in any circumstance.

The next time a door opens your way, don't waste time and leave your small mark in the history of the world. It is through simple bold gestures that lasting happiness is built.
